OL,3,CRishi Sunak sending mixed signals on
OL,4,Cclimate change, say official advisers
OL,6,FThe Government is not doing enough to
OL,7,Fmeet its climate change obligations
OL,8,Fand the Prime Minister has "sent mixed
OL,9,Fsignals" to international partners,
OL,10,Fhis official advisers have warned.
OL,12,FThe Climate Change Committee said
OL,13,Fperception of the UK around the world
OL,14,Fas a leader on green issues was hit
OL,15,Fafter Rishi Sunak weakened some of the
OL,16,Fcountry's policies.
