OL,3,CRishi Sunak sending mixed signals on
OL,4,Cclimate change, say official advisers
OL,6,F"The international perception of the
OL,7,FUK's climate ambition suffered from
OL,8,Fmixed messages following announcements
OL,9,Fon new fossil fuel developments and
OL,10,Fthe Prime Minister's speech to soften
OL,11,Fsome net zero policies," the committee
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FIt came in a report from the group
OL,15,Finto the progress made at the Cop28
OL,16,Fsummit in the United Arab Emirates in
OL,17,FDecember.
