OL,3,CRishi Sunak sending mixed signals on
OL,4,Cclimate change, say official advisers
OL,6,FAs the world faced the hottest year on
OL,7,Frecord and carbon dioxide emissions
OL,8,Freached their highest level,
OL,9,Fnegotiators made some progress at the
OL,10,Fmeeting, the committee said, but the
OL,11,FUK's role at the forefront of global
OL,12,Fefforts to fight climate change was
OL,13,Fdamaged.
OL,15,F"The Prime Minister's net zero speech
OL,16,Fin September 2023, and decisions to
OL,17,Fapprove a new coal mine and license
OL,18,Fnew oil and gas production, have
OL,19,Fcontributed to a perception of slowing
OL,20,FUK climate ambition by members of the
OL,21,Finternational community," it said.
OL,26,@wD@AOU}D@YO]
