OL,3,CRishi Sunak sending mixed signals on
OL,4,Cclimate change, say official advisers
OL,6,F"This is despite subsequent positive
OL,7,Fpolicy announcements."
OL,9,FThe positive announcements include a
OL,10,Frule which effectively forces car and
OL,11,Fvan manufacturers to ensure a
OL,12,FGovernment-mandated proportion of
OL,13,Ftheir vehicles are electric.
OL,15,FThere was also extra help for
OL,16,Fhouseholds to switch away from gas
OL,17,Fboilers and towards heat pumps, which
OL,18,Frun off electricity.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@VO]
