OL,3,CRishi Sunak sending mixed signals on
OL,4,Cclimate change, say official advisers
OL,6,FBut the committee called for much more
OL,7,Faction to ensure the UK meets interim
OL,8,Fgoals along the way to become net zero
OL,9,Fby 2050.
OL,11,FIt said renewables had to be rapidly
OL,12,Fdeployed, adding that the rollout of
OL,13,Fsolar panels and onshore wind turbines
OL,14,Fis "progressing too slowly" because
OL,15,Fthere are barriers in the planning
OL,16,Fregime and it takes too long to link
OL,17,Fto the electricity grid.
OL,19,FThe Government and National Grid have
OL,20,Frecently started taking steps to speed
OL,21,Fup grid connections.
OL,26,@vD@DOUvD@[O]
