OL,3,CRishi Sunak sending mixed signals on
OL,4,Cclimate change, say official advisers
OL,6,FThe committee also said the Government
OL,7,Fshould limit more oil and gas from
OL,8,Fbeing produced from UK waters.
OL,10,F"Were all countries with fossil fuel
OL,11,Freserves to increase future fossil
OL,12,Ffuel production, there would be an
OL,13,Foversupply that would pose a risk to
OL,14,Fthe aims of the Paris Agreement," it
OL,15,Fsaid.
