OL,3,CRishi Sunak sending mixed signals on
OL,4,Cclimate change, say official advisers
OL,6,FThe committee said the rate of
OL,7,Femissions reductions must quadruple
OL,8,Ffrom 1.2% to 4.7% a year, excluding
OL,9,Felectricity supply, and that tree
OL,10,Fplanting and peatland restoration
OL,11,F"have been too slow and urgently
OL,12,Frequire scaling up to meet UK
OL,13,Femissions reduction targets".
OL,15,FProfessor Piers Forster, interim
OL,16,Fchairman of the Climate Change
OL,17,FCommittee, said: "The UK played an
OL,18,Fimportant role in this hard-fought
OL,19,FCop28 outcome.
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@\O]yD@ROU
