OL,3,CRishi Sunak sending mixed signals on
OL,4,Cclimate change, say official advisers
OL,6,F"We may be further into the
OL,7,Fdecarbonisation journey than many
OL,8,Fnations, but the obligation on every
OL,9,Fcountry is now to push even harder.
OL,11,F"This also frames the economic
OL,12,Fchallenge for the UK. We must rapidly
OL,13,Freplace fossil fuels with low-carbon
OL,14,Falternatives to get back on track to
OL,15,Fmeet our 2030 goal.
OL,17,F"The UK could set a powerful example
OL,18,Fof tackling climate change and
OL,19,Freducing our insecurity to climate
OL,20,Fimpacts.
