OL,3,CRishi Sunak sending mixed signals on
OL,4,Cclimate change, say official advisers
OL,6,F"The new global adaptation framework
OL,7,Fgoes further than our own so I urge
OL,8,Fthe Government to lean into its global
OL,9,Frole with an even stronger
OL,10,Fdemonstration of domestic ambition."
OL,12,FThe Government said: "The UK is
OL,13,Fleading international action,
OL,14,Fdelivering an agreement to transition
OL,15,Faway from fossil fuels and as one of
OL,16,Fthe largest contributors to the loss
OL,17,Fand damage fund.
