OL,3,CRishi Sunak sending mixed signals on
OL,4,Cclimate change, say official advisers
OL,6,F"We are the first major economy to
OL,7,Fhalve our emissions, have some of the
OL,8,Fworld's most ambitious legally binding
OL,9,Ftargets, and have over delivered on
OL,10,Fevery carbon budget to date, while our
OL,11,Fsignificant investment in the UK's
OL,12,Fworld-leading clean energy sector `
OL,13,Fwith 40% of our electricity now
OL,14,Frenewable compared to just 7% in 2010
OL,15,F` is bolstering our energy security."
